Name: cups
Version: 1.0b5
Release: 0
Copyright: GPL
Group: System Environment/Daemons
Source: ftp://ftp.easysw.com/pub/cups/beta/cups-1.0b5-source.tar.gz
Url: http://www.cups.org
Packager: Michael Sweet <mike@easysw.com>
